This is a git repo

library to install:
sudo apt-get install librxtx-java

to execute:
java -jar target/restprj-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar

to enable/disable debug:
touch /tmp/hal900debug
rm /tmp/hal900debug

to browse:
GET:
http://localhost:8080/hal9000/test
http://localhost:8080/hal9000/clock

POST:
http://localhost:8080/hal9000/debug?enable=true
http://localhost:8080/hal9000/setclock
